{"type": "article", "id": 26611, "title": "用激光表现时间流逝的钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-10T06:52:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171514U17X6BxvWfKGzTs3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">还记得我们去年介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/16967.html\">一款沙子钟</a>吗？这一次，<a href=\"http://ayaskan.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Studio Ayaskan</a> 将介质转变为了液体，以激光在水中射出的痕迹作为指针，紫色的线条须臾间就在水中消散。相比以小时显示时刻的沙子钟，这款 Trace clock 看上去多了一份不确定性，也更好地表现出时间的飞速流逝。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171512ELKWygF6SAs0ecJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171512xBAFeKZC13wYcgm9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171513kixga83CG1ebR5cK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171513AZsx0p76k1Qvr4GE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}